text: Falköpings KIK is a sports club in Falköping, Sweden. The club was established in 1976. In 2007, the women's soccer team played in the Swedish top division, Damallsvenskan. == References == ==Other website== * Falköpings KIK - Official website Category:1976 establishments in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs
